com.github.nfcforandroid.api

Interface INfaParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidApplicationParser, ExternalParser, MimeTypeParser, NdefParser, NfaParserAdapter, SmartPosterParser, TextExternalParser, TextParser, UnknownParser, UnsupportedParser, UriExternalParser, UriParser

    public interface INfaParser
    Author:
    jefBinomed This interface is used when you want to read datas. You should implement this interface when you want to add a new way to parse a special INfaRecord A set of implementations exists in the nfa-parsers module
